OL,3,CCoroner finds death of baby was
OL,4,Cavoidable
OL,6,FA coroner has ruled that the death of
OL,7,Fa baby boy in Craigavon Area Hospital
OL,8,Fwas avoidable.
OL,10,FTroy Brady was born in August 2016 and
OL,11,Fdied in the neonatal unit six days
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FOutside court on Friday, the family's
OL,15,Fsolicitor read a statement on their
OL,16,Fbehalf.
