OL,6,F"We believed then and we believe now
OL,7,Fthat there were failings in the care
OL,8,Fprovided both before and during Troy's
OL,9,Ftraumatic birth," said Lawrence
OL,10,FMcMahon.
OL,12,F"It is our wish that no other family
OL,13,Fshould have to endure the pain and
OL,14,Floss we have had to endure.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
