OL,6,F"Our loss continues. We hope that as a
OL,7,Fresult of the inquest into Troy's
OL,8,Fdeath that Craigavon Area Hospital and
OL,9,Fthe Southern Health and Social Care
OL,10,FTrust will put in place improved
OL,11,Fprocedures and safeguards for dealing
OL,12,Fwith expectant mothers and high-risk
OL,13,Fbirths.
OL,15,F"We believe that fully-informed
OL,16,Fconsent should form the basis of trust
OL,17,Fbetween medical staff and expectant
OL,18,Fparents."
