OL,6,FThe coroner also stated that the
OL,7,Fdoctor in the delivery room lacked
OL,8,Fexperience and competence to perform
OL,9,Fthe procedure he was carrying out.
OL,11,FShe also recommended that all hospital
OL,12,Ftrusts should provide parents with
OL,13,Fmore information to make informed
OL,14,Fchoices on natural and caesarian
OL,15,Fbirths.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Southern Health
OL,18,FTrust extended its deepest sympathies
OL,19,Fto the Brady family.
