OL,6,FIt said it had participated fully in
OL,7,Fthe inquest process and accepted the
OL,8,Fcoroner's findings, and said it would
OL,9,Freview the coroner's written findings
OL,10,Fin detail when completed.
OL,12,FIt said in recent years, it had made
OL,13,Fchanges to procedures regarding
OL,14,Fcommunication between staff and
OL,15,Ffamilies particularly around delivery
OL,16,Foptions.
